name: The Wanderer
description:
The Wanderer is the ultimate traveller of the Tapestry.
Wrapped in a tattered mantle and wielding a strange crooked cane, His existence seems to be devoted to a single purpose: treading every path the realm of realms has to offer; a task that transcends time and space.
Most fear his presence but the truly adventurous welcome it, for they know that every path that He has recently trod on is one where horror and danger will have no place.
